Title: Judas Priest
Plot: Vic and his crew track down the Russian who was involved with the cop murders, but they lose control during his interrogation and the hit man dies in an explosion before they can get any answers.  Meanwhile, Aceveda  is blackmailed by the man who assaaulted him.  Plus, Rawling's seizure is on the verge of being shelved.
Writer: Kurt Sutter, Charles H. Eglee, Scott Rosenbaum
GuestStars: Anthony Anderson, David Marciano, Nigel Gibbs, Camillia Sanes, Rebecca Pidgeon, Darrow Igus, Cathy Lind Hayes, Cliff Weissman, RonReaco Lee, Kurt Caceres, Faleolo Alailima
